Hutchison Fundraiser Attached is an invitation to a fundraiser for Senator Kay Bailey Hutchison It is at Mesa Grill on West Gray on August Food and entertainment by Jack Ingram is included Please call me at work or at home if you have any questions Hope to see you there Kara Howes Katherine K Howes Bracewell Patterson LLP fax Message from Joseph A Manero on Thu Jul To UndisclosedRecipient UndisclosedRecipient Subject Hutchison event invitation I have attached the invitation for the Aug Kay Bailey HutchisonJack Ingram event at Mesa Grill The file can be viewed using the Adobe Acrobat Reader If you do not have the Reader installed on your computer you can download it for free from the following address productsacrobatreadstephtml productsacrobatreadstephtml To send the invitation to your guestsinvitees you may wish to use it as a file attachment in an email to them or you may wish to print it and fax it to them individually It is designed in such a way to fax in a very clean manner Please let me know if you have any trouble with the file Please instruct your guestsinvitees to mail their checks as soon as possible in order to get an accurate head count prior to the event The address is on the invitation but here it is again KBH Mesa Event PO Box Houston TX Thank you for your hard work to make the event a great success Please call me if you have any questions Joseph A Manero Principal The Ayes of Texas Political Consulting Public Affairs Main Street Suite Houston Texas Voice Fax

FarewellI just wanted to take a minute to bid you farewell This will be my last week at Enron as I have accepted a job with Kinder Morgan Energy Partners and will be starting there next Monday I enjoyed working with each of you during my time at Enron and hope to keep in touch I am not sure what my email will be at Kinder Morgan but you can always reach me at Take care and stay in touch Dax Dax A Sanders Associate Bandwidth Origination Enron Broadband Services Work Cell
